data.description: This captivating home, built in 1999, offers a delightful blend of comfort and space. Boasting 3,083 sq ft of living area, this residence presents an ideal opportunity for those seeking a generous layout and modern features.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open concept design that seamlessly connects the kitchen and living room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is well-appointed, featuring ample cabinetry, sleek countertops, and modern appliances, making it a chef's delight.    With four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home is designed to accommodate a growing family or provide flexible space for guests and hobbies. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a spacious layout and a large walk-in closet, offering a perfect haven for relaxation.    Beyond the bedrooms, you'll discover three separate living rooms, providing abundant space for entertaining, hosting gatherings, or simply enjoying quiet moments with loved ones. Additionally, an upstairs loft adds versatility, ideal for use as a home office, media room, or play area.    The property also benefits from its location in a neighborhood without an HOA, offering freedom and flexibility for homeowners. The bedrooms are of good size, providing comfort and privacy for all family members or guests.  this home offers a desirable combination of convenience and serenity. The surrounding area provides access to an array of amenities, including parks, schools, shopping centers, and recreational opportunities. Additionally, its proximity to major highways and freeways ensures easy commuting to neighboring cities.    This beautiful home presents an incredible opportunity to own a spacious, well-maintained home in Hemet, CA. With its open concept design, multiple living areas, generous bedrooms, and a prime location, this property is a gem waiting to be discovered. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home!    Find lovely parks conveniently located at walking distance.
